Odaily Planet Daily News BNB Chain announced the latest list of BNB Hack winning projects. This selection covers submissions from May 25 to June 5, 2025, and received more than 30 project applications. In the end, the AI ​​proxy tool market MCPForge was selected as a Tier 3 winning project, receiving a $3,000 prize, a $50,000 startup support package, and a BNB Chain channel display opportunity. In addition, four projects, Quest Craft, Akai Space, Expiry Mitra, and NeuroBalance, were selected as potential Tier 4 winners.
The above 5 projects are briefly introduced as follows:
MCPForge: A crypto-native AI agent tool market that transforms GitHub-based MCP Repos into deployable, callable and monetizable AI services, simplifying the path from code to income;
Quest Craft: A play-and-earn Minecraft server where players can link crypto wallets, complete AI-generated tasks, and earn soul-bound crypto tokens through real-world and in-game utilities;
Akai Space: A gamified data labeling platform that combines Web3 incentives, AI-assisted annotations, and Play-to-Earn mechanisms to provide scalable, high-quality datasets for AI development;
Expiry Mitra: An AI-driven decentralized tool that enables pharmacies and consumers to instantly verify the authenticity of drugs and combat counterfeit drugs;
NeuroBalance: An AI portfolio manager on the BNB Smart Chain that automatically rebalances crypto assets using machine learning and customizable strategies.
